profile.profileDescription: Use this profile if you want a system that is compliant with cataloguing SHPO collected historic property information.

label.name_singular: SC Department of Archives and History Collection
label.name_plural: SC Department of Archives and History Collections

label.name_singular: South Carolina Department of Archives and History
label.name_plural: South Carolina Department of Archives and History

label.name: Control Number
label.description: A unique id assigned to a surveyed historic property. It is composed of the status/county number/site number.

label.name: Tax Number
label.description: A property tax number assigned by the county in which the historic property resides.

label.name: Historical Use
label.description: Denotes the original or past use of the historic property.

label.name: Current Use
label.description: Denotes the current use of the historic property.

label.name: National Register Designation
label.description: Denotes the designation of the property/site in the National Register of Historic Places.

label.name: Architect/Builder
label.description: Gives the name of the architect(s) and/or builder(s).

label.name: Stories
label.description: Gives the number of stories/floors the historic property is tall.

label.name: Construction Method
label.description: Describes the method with which the property was constructed.

label.name: Exterior Walls
label.description: Describes the composition and appearance of the exterior walls.

label.name: Foundation
label.description: Describes the composition and appearance of the foundation of the property.

label.name: Roof Shape
label.description: Describes the shape of the roof.

label.name: Roof Materials
label.description: Denotes the materials used to construct the roof.

label.name: Porch Width
label.description: Denotes the width of the porch if one is present at the historic property.

label.name: Porch Shape
label.description: Describes the shape of the porch if one is present at the historic property.

label.name: Significant Architectural Features
label.description: Describes any signficant architectural features of the historic property.

label.name: Alterations
label.description: Describes any alterations made to the historic property over time.

label.name: Historical Information
label.description: A detailed description of any background or historical information about the property, its use, or its inhabitants.

label.name: Historical Information Source
label.description: Citations for the source(s) of historical information regarding the property.

label.name: National Register Site Listing
label.description: A hyperlink that leads the user to the SCDAH's National Registry website for a listed site.

label.name: Ownership
label.description: Denotes the current ownership status of the historic property.

label.name: Core Property Shape
label.description: Describes the core shape of the historic property.

label.name: Historic Property Category
label.description: Denotes the type of historic property.

label.name: Architectural Form
label.description: Denotes the architectural form of the historic property.

label.name: Architectural Style
label.description: Denotes the architectural style of the historic property.

label.name: Street Address
label.description: The street Address of the historic property or district.

label.name: Location Description
label.description: Use this field for general directions that denote a property location. e.g., 3 miles past the cotton farm. Do not use this field if a specific address is provided.

label.name: City
label.description: Denotes the city/town/village in which a property is located.

label.name: County
label.description: Denotes the county in which a property is located.

label.name: Quadrant Name
label.description: The name of the quadrant in which the property is located.

label.name: Date Constructed
label.description: The date/date range during which the property was built.

label.name: Date Altered
label.description: The date/date range during which the property was altered.

label.name: Date of Significance
label.description: The date/date range during which the property was significant.

label.name: Historic Resources Survey
label.description: Metadata describing the historic resources survey under which the historic property was recorded.

label.name: Recorded By
label.description: The name of the individual or group who completed the historic resources survey for this historic property.

label.name: Survey Type
label.description: Denotes the type of historical properties survey that was conducted.

label.name: Report Location
label.description: Denotes the archival box location of the survey report.

label.name: Digital Object Information
label.description: Metadata describing the digital representation of the historic property site survey card.

label.name: File Name
label.description: The string of characters that indentify a computer file. Do not include the file extension in this field.

label.name: Date Digitized
label.description: The date on which the site survey card was digitized by the SCDAH.

label.name: File Format
label.description: The file extension of the digitized file. E.g. JPG, TIFF, PDF.

label.name: DPI
label.description: Dots per inch (DPI) measurement of the digitized site survey card. Only enter the number. E.g., for 600 DPI, only enter 600.

label.name: Digitized By
label.description: The name of staff member, intern, or volunteer who digitized the site survey card.

label.name: Scanner
label.description: The name of the scanner used. E.g., "ScanSnap ix500"

label.name: National Register Designation
label.description: Denotes the designation of a district in the National Register of Historic Places.

label.name: National Register Site Listing
label.description: A hyperlink that leads the user to the SCDAH's National Registry website for a listed district.

label.name: Catalog Hyperlink
label.description: A hyperlink that leads the user to the SCDAH's catalog listing for an archival collection.

label.name: Archival Collection Number
label.description: Number of the unique collection in the SC Department of Archives and History.

label.name: Date Recorded
label.description: The date this historic property was recorded in the historic resources survey.

label.typename: is contained in the archival collection
